descriptions:
Matthew Weier O'Phinney is a
      web professional and architect, technical writer, and speaker. Matthew
      works as a Principal Engineer at Zend
        Technologies (a RogueWave
        company, where he leads the Zend Framework and Apigility
      projects, providing open source tools for building web applications and
      APIs in PHP. He blogs at https://mwop.net/blog
      and is @mwop on Twitter.
